2005-09-27  a3schuur

	* httpAdapter.c: Bug [ 1298807 ] sfcb dos vulnerability Next step
	to detect and reject DOS attacks.  Fist data after accept must
	arrive within 5 seconds, otherwise the request will be rejected.

2005-09-27  a3schuur

	* httpAdapter.c: Bug [ 1298807 ] sfcb dos vulnerability First steps
	to detect and reject DOS attacks.  a) None POST requests will be
	rejected as early as possible without attempting to read remaining
	HTTP header data.  b) Any request having a combined header data
	size longer than 5000 bytes will be rejected

